{
  "name": "CYRUS - AI Dossier Generation",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "generate-dossier",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "webhook-trigger",
      "name": "Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [250, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "=https://api.shodan.io/shodan/host/search?key={{ $env.SHODAN_API_KEY }}&query=hostname:{{ $node[\"Webhook\"].json.body.websiteUrl.replace(/^https?:\\/\\//, '').replace(/^www\\./, '') }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "shodan-recon",
      "name": "Shodan Recon",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [450, 300],
      "continueOnFail": true
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "={{ $env.AI_MODEL || \"gemini-2.0-flash\" }}",
        "prompt": "=Generate a comprehensive Cyber Risk Dossier for the organization: {{ $node[\"Webhook\"].json.body.organizationName }}. \n\nTarget Website: {{ $node[\"Webhook\"].json.body.websiteUrl }}\n\nIMPORTANT: You are a professional cyber risk analyst. Synthesize a structured JSON object matching the cyrus_dossier schema. \n\nTECHNICAL CONTEXT (Shodan OSINT):\n{{ JSON.stringify($json) }}\n\nFALLBACK INSTRUCTIONS:\n- If Technical OSINT data is sparse, empty, or unreachable, use your pre-trained general knowledge of this organization to provide a deep threat narrative.\n- Focus on real-world HQ locations, leadership, and revenue scale.\n- Ensure the 'narrative' field is professional, objective, and detailed.\n- Return ONLY the JSON object.",
        "options": {
          "responseMimeType": "application/json"
        }
      },
      "id": "gemini-dossier-builder",
      "name": "Gemini Dossier Builder",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [650, 300],
      "credentials": {
        "googleGeminiApi": {
          "id": "Google Gemini API"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "options": {
          "responseCode": 200,
          "responseBody": "={{ $json }}"
        }
      },
      "id": "respond-to-webhook",
      "name": "Respond to Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [850, 300]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Webhook": { "main": [[{ "node": "shodan-recon", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "shodan-recon": { "main": [[{ "node": "gemini-dossier-builder", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "gemini-dossier-builder": { "main": [[{ "node": "respond-to-webhook", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] }
  },
  "active": true,
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  },
  "versionId": "2",
  "id": "2",
  "meta": { "templateId": "cyrus-dossier-generation" }
}
